<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Reply to Your Question</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>You have received a reply to your question in the video "<%= title %>",</p>
        <p>Please login to our website to view the full discussion</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>